@Zeichen32 no, it cannot be the same bug. A PUT request is not doing a partial binding of the form, and this bug is about partial binding.
I think your issue is #8261, and the solution is given: https://github.com/symfony/symfony/issues/8261?source=cc#issuecomment-19882153

